<typeStatus id="549C26967E54FFD8FB3C76F1DBE9FA08" box="[1219,1271,1499,1523]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">type</typeStatus>
species name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9898347E54FFD8FF3F7521DDDDF9D8" blockId="38.[192,707,1547,1572]" box="[192,707,1547,1572]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis id="B95344267E54FFD8FF3F7521DEAEF9D8" bold="true" box="[192,432,1547,1571]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">Species included.</emphasis>
Only the 
<typeStatus id="549C26967E54FFD8FDD67526DD40F9DF" box="[553,606,1548,1572]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">type</typeStatus>
species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9898347E54FFD8FF3F7516DC21F9AF" blockId="38.[192,831,1596,1620]" box="[192,831,1596,1620]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">
